---
<section id="dataset" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Dataset References</h2>
    
    <div class="dataset-content">
      <p>The model development workflow is documented in the Kaggle notebook. The dataset used for CropCheckUp experiments and training is available on Kaggle.</p>
      
      <div class="reference-links">
        <a href="https://www.kaggle.com/code/rasagyavatsal/cropcheckup" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Kaggle Notebook</h3>
            <p>Model development workflow and experimentation.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/rasagyavatsal/cropcheckup-dataset" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>CropCheckUp Dataset</h3>
            <p>Image dataset used for CropCheckUp experiments and training.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dataset-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .dataset-content > p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .reference-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-m);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .reference-links {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .resource-card {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-subtle-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-l);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .resource-card:hover, .resource-card:focus-visible {
    background-color: var(--color-raised-surface);
    border-color: var(--color-brand);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .card-content h3 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs) 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--color-brand);
  }

  .card-content p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .arrow {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--color-brand);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .resource-card:hover .arrow, .resource-card:focus-visible .arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>
